# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# This folder contains following files:
#    employeeapp.tcl  - Main application
#    employee.tcl     - Defines Employee object
#    address.tcl      - Defines Address object
#    saveemployee.tcl - Defines a transaction to add/save Employee and
#                       Address objects
#    employee.db      - Pre-configured SQLite3 database with employee
#                       address tables
# 
# Before running this demo, please clear any existing records from
# employee and address tables in employee.db by issuing following
# commands in sqlite3 client:
#
#    sqlite3 employee.db
#    delete from addr;
#    delete from employee;
#    .exit
#
# To see the log messages, in shell prompt, issue the following command:
#
#    tail -f employee.log
#
# To run this application, in another shell, issue the following
# command:
#
#    tclsh employeeapp.tcl
#
